implements all the rpc’s defined in the \sphinxtitleref{common/leotest.proto} protocol
definition. Incoming rpc requests are verified by {\hyperref[\detokenize{orchestrator:orchestrator.orchestrator.CheckToken}]{\sphinxcrossref{\sphinxcode{\sphinxupquote{CheckToken}}}}}
before being invoked.
